Class StorageUnit

  • java.lang.Object
    • model.common.Model
      • model.productcontainer.ProductContainer
        • model.productcontainer.StorageUnit
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, IModel

    public class StorageUnit
extends ProductContainer
    The StorageUnit class encapsulates all the funtions and data associated with a "StorageUnit". It extends the ProductContainer implements the general functions for StorageUnit and for ProductGroup.
